'''Tan II''', pronounced Tan 2, is a type of [[rubber]] that was used in [[golf ball]]s, it was replaced by Supersport and is not currently produced anymore. Tan II is still considered by many flyers to be the very best type of rubber band for model airplane flying.{{Citation needed|date=November 2007}}

